content.rendered:
Blush Palette

  • Apply directly to the apples of your cheeks using your preferred blush colour to give the cheekbones a polished look.

Contour Palette

  • Create the appearance of lifted cheekbones by gently sweeping the contour colour in the hollows of your cheeks.
  • Blend the tones with your makeup brush for a smooth colour gradient
